#!/usr/bin/perl
use Poet::App;
Poet::App->run;

__END__

=pod

=head1 NAME

poet - main Poet command-line interface

=head1 SYNOPSIS

   poet new [-d dir] [-q] <AppName>

   poet script <script_name>

=head1 DESCRIPTION

For general help, run C<poet help>.

For help with a specific command, run C<poet help _subcommand_>.

=head1 SEE ALSO    

Poet

